### ============================================================
###  HOTEL AVAILABILITY API  —  VS Code REST Client Script
###  Install: "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
###  Click "Send Request" above any ### block
### ============================================================

@baseUrl   = http://localhost:5000
@hotelId   = 12345678
@fromDate  = 2026-03-20
@toDate    = 2026-03-25


# ============================================================
# 1. CHECK AVAILABILITY — single hotel
#    GET /check/hotels/room-availability
#    Required: hotelId, fromDate, toDate
#    Returns: actualAvailableRooms, isAvailable, bookingSummary
# ============================================================

### Check single hotel availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/hotels/room-availability?hotelId={{hotelId}}&fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate={{toDate}}

###
### Missing hotelId → expect 400 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/hotels/room-availability?fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate={{toDate}}

###
### Invalid date → expect 400 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/hotels/room-availability?hotelId={{hotelId}}&fromDate=not-a-date&toDate={{toDate}}

###
### toDate before fromDate → expect 400 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/hotels/room-availability?hotelId={{hotelId}}&fromDate=2026-03-25&toDate=2026-03-20

###
### Hotel not found → expect 404 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/hotels/room-availability?hotelId=00000000&fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate={{toDate}}


# ============================================================
# 2. FIND ALL AVAILABLE HOTELS
#    GET /check/all-hotels/room-availability
#    Required: fromDate, toDate
#    Optional: city (case-sensitive)
#    Returns: array of hotels with actualAvailableRooms, isAvailable
# ============================================================

### Get all available hotels (no city filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate={{toDate}}

###
### Filter by city
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate={{toDate}}&city=Mumbai

###
### Weekend availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?fromDate=2026-03-22&toDate=2026-03-24

###
### Long stay (1 week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?fromDate={{fromDate}}&toDate=2026-03-27

###
### Missing fromDate → expect 400 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?toDate={{toDate}}

###
### toDate same as fromDate → expect 400 error (must be strictly after)
GET {{baseUrl}}/check/all-hotels/room-availability?fromDate=2026-03-20&toDate=2026-03-20
